{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 1570116, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 308895, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "同左吧，可能能理解", "timestamp": 1619846098, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1570125, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 308895, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "他不敢", "timestamp": 1619846160, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1570126, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 308895, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "毕竟他的父亲是中共八老，和某些伤痕文人的立足点根本不一样，没有了中共他就泯然众人矣叻。薄熙来老师在文革中还踹断他老爹三根肋骨呢，不照样红歌唱的开心，文革余孽继续当嘛", "timestamp": 1619846168, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1570130, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 308895, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "因为他比谁都明白，国家是人民的国家，文革是人民的选择", "timestamp": 1619846199, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1570136, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 308895, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "受到迫害还可以上清华呢", "timestamp": 1619846219, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1570145, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 308895, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "哪怕是在文革下乡期间，他老可以去四川考察怎么建化粪池，这也是靠了习仲勋老师的路子才得以成行的。就算是被迫害，不同人还是不同命的。去夹边沟的和去五七干校的都是号称自己是被迫害的，他们的待遇能一样吗", "timestamp": 1619846285, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1570164, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 308895, "reply_to": 1570145, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 谁都说自己被迫害，但下了乡和进了清华能一样吗？？？", "timestamp": 1619846521, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1570167, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 308895, "reply_to": 1570126, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 薄熙来那个纯属谣传", "timestamp": 1619846530, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1570213, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 308895, "reply_to": 1570164, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: 所以说嘛，老剧说得好：“你爷爷一犯错，我爷爷就挨饿”。尽管很有可能将来会说你爷爷和我爷爷都是受迫害的，但两个爷爷还是不一样的", "timestamp": 1619846813, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1570333, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 308895, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "清华在线接收被迫害男孩", "timestamp": 1619847819, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1570479, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Hans", "pid": 308895, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "因为他发现，这种让别人敢怒不敢言还要高呼万岁的感觉，真的很爽", "timestamp": 1619849462, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1577032, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Isabella", "pid": 308895, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "还是我们的孩子好，至少不会扬了我们祖坟.jpg", "timestamp": 1619950786, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 10, "pid": 308895, "reply": 12, "tag": "政治相关", "text": "大大的父亲和他也在文革中受到了迫害，为什么没有像一些伤痕文人一样对国家充满不满？", "timestamp": 1619845927, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1619950784, "url": "", "vote": {}}}